<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA12">
<l>aṟiveṉṉun tāḷkoḷuvi yaimpulaṉun tammiṟ</l>
<l>ceṟiveṉṉun tiṇkatavañ cemmi – maṟaiyeṉṟu</l>
<l>naṉkōti naṉkuṇarvār kāṇparē nāṭōṟum</l>
<l>paiṅkōta vaṇṇaṉ paṭi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who perceive [him] well, well reciting what is called Veda, putting the bolt</l>
<l>called knowledge [and] closing the firm door called restraining</l>
<l>all five senses in themselves, they will see every day</l>
<l>the form of him with the colour of the fresh flood.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
